{"metadata":{"role":"symbol","externalID":"s:16OUDSThemesOrange0B31ThemeTagComponentTokensProviderC","roleHeading":"Class","title":"OrangeThemeTagComponentTokensProvider","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"OrangeThemeTagComponentTokensProvider"}],"modules":[{"name":"OUDSThemesOrange"}],"symbolKind":"class","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"class"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OrangeThemeTagComponentTokensProvider"}]},"kind":"symbol","sections":[],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeTagComponentTokensProvider","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"relationshipsSections":[{"title":"Conforms To","kind":"relationships","type":"conformsTo","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDS\/documentation\/OUDS\/AllTagComponentTokensProvider","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/19OUDSTokensComponent03TagB6TokensP","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/s8CopyableP","doc:\/\/OUDS\/documentation\/OUDS\/TokensProvider"]}],"abstract":[{"text":"A class which wraps all ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"component  tokens of tag","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":" for ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"tag","type":"text"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"text":" objects like ","type":"text"},{"code":"OUDSTag","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":".","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Contains also references to semantic tokens providers so as to be able to use them to define the component tokens.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"This provider should be integrated as a ","type":"text"},{"code":"AllTagComponentTokensProvider","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" implementation inside ","type":"text"},{"code":"OUDSTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" so as to provide","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"all tokens to the users. It helps users to override some of the tokens and assign them to an ","type":"text"},{"code":"OUDSTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" implementation to use.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Custom themes can use subclass of ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeTagComponentTokensProvider","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":" and apply the provider they need.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"It implements also the protocol ","type":"text"},{"code":"TagComponentTokens","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" so as to expose the component tokens for ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"tags"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"text":" through any ","type":"text"},{"code":"OUDSTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":".","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Tags"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"text":" components tokens are defined with semantic tokens of colors (from ","type":"text"},{"code":"AllColorSemanticTokensProvider","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":"),","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"sizes (from ","type":"text"},{"code":"AllSizeSemanticTokensProvider","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":"), spaces (from ","type":"text"},{"code":"AllSpaceSemanticTokensProvider","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":") and borders","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"(from ","type":"text"},{"code":"AllBorderSemanticTokensProvider","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":").","type":"text"}],"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["macOS"],"tokens":[{"text":"class","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OrangeThemeTagComponentTokensProvider","kind":"identifier"}]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"text":"Overview","anchor":"overview","level":2,"type":"heading"},{"code":["    \/\/ Define your own provider for tag component tokens","    \/\/ by inheriting from existing provider","    class CustomTagComponentTokensProvider: OrangeThemeTagComponentTokensProvider {","","        \/\/ Then override the tag component tokens you want."